{"tid":1687313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[非割蓆]希望各位手足唔好裝修無障礙設施","createTime":"2019-11-01T17:37:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:35:04.000Z","uid":34978,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c07ec26596b84d626eab13b9dcc9660114e5c9a","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:37:53.000Z","msg":"之前都有巴打開過類似嘅post<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n小小請求，非割蓆，拆鐵可唔可以唔好拆升降機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656176\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656176</a><br />\n<br />\n手足可唔可以唔好搞Lift...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1547242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1547242</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">又話罷鐵，仲搭黨鐵？搭巴士啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n大家要罷鐵都仲有好多選擇（巴士、小巴）<br />\n但輪椅人士交通工具選擇真係有限<br />\n無疑黨鐵真係最方便<br />\n我自己嚟講，因為常去嘅站架𨋢被裝修咗<br />\n呢排已經轉咗搭巴士<br />\n我自己算好彩附近有呢條巴士線<br />\n但好多時啲地方未必可以一程巴士去到，甚至要轉小巴<br />\n<br />\n同埋巴士大部分都只可以上一架輪椅<br />\n如果車上已經有一架，又要等下班車<br />\n（經醫院嗰啲巴士線真係會好多輪椅搭）<br />\n而且要司機較低車身，再落車放低塊地台<br />\n巴士司機有幾chur大家都知<br />\n幫一幫輪椅客上落可能自己就少咗時間休息<br />\n所以有時啲司機態度可能冇咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我哋自己都會有hard feeling<br />\n而搭黨鐵唔少輪椅都可以自己上落車<br />\n相對上係方便好多<br />\n<br />\n而且有時唔只係裝修黨鐵𨋢<br />\n仲有政府嘅𨋢（例如天橋嗰啲）<br />\n去到嗰啲位先發現冇𨋢搭真係企（坐）咗喺到<br />\n又要唔知點行/行幾耐先去到目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">又話攬炒？少少犧牲都做唔到？</span></span></strong><br />\n攬炒係炒哂全世界<br />\n但𨋢冇得用，就淨係得行動不便人士/銀髮族/（推bb車嘅人）受影響<br />\n而且黨鐵係大條道理唔整返好佢住<br />\n因為可能整完好快又爛<br />\n而一向如果啲站整𨋢，佢哋會安排車你去下一個站<br />\n但而家又係大條道理乜安排都冇<br />\n平時整𨋢，就算冇安排車，最多自己行去下一個站<br />\n但而家好多係連續幾個站都冇𨋢搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且有部分人可能未必咁理智認清問題根源<br />\n可能會覺得示威者阻住佢<br />\n失去部分中立/淺黃嘅支持（情況有啲似塞鐵）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲時勢行動不便就唔好岀咁多街啦</span></strong></span><br />\n其實好多行動不便嘅朋友/銀髮族都要定期去覆診<br />\n唔少都要返工返學<br />\n唔係話唔岀就唔岀咁簡單<br />\n甚至有啲會去遊行發夢，係同路人<br />\n（銀髮族幾落力大家都見到）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵都閂站㗎啦，有冇𨋢仲有乜分別？</span></strong></span><br />\n黨鐵而家除咗有行動會閂站同夜晚早咗閂<br />\n其餘時間，包括上述好多人要岀街嘅覆診同返放工時間<br />\n大部分都係有開的<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係同路人的話，連登巴絲夾錢俾佢哋搭的士又點話</span></span></strong><br />\n好多謝一眾巴絲咁有心<br />\n但其實即使的士都唔夠鐵方便<br />\n唔係錢嘅問題，係上落車唔方便<br />\n甚至有啲用電動輪椅嘅朋友係過唔到凳的<br />\n除非係星群的士嗰種<br />\n但真係比較貴<br />\n返工返學日日咁搭都唔係好實際<br />\n同路人的話一嚟唔好意思收大家錢<br />\n二嚟都希望啲錢幫返有需要嘅義士<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">復康巴呢？</span></span></strong><br />\n復康巴都係要預約<br />\n而且要提早好多book的（以月計）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當初入立法會<br />\n手足們都會保護文物，唔會無差別破壞<br />\n因為大家都唔係暴徒，會保持理智<br />\n我希望大家都可以考慮吓我呢個post講嘅嘢<br />\n但我重申一次，呢個絕對唔係割蓆post<br />\n就算𨋢爛哂都唔會割<br />\n會清楚記得係邊個搞到而家咁嘅局面<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d04c07ef0a80d4e8bdaaf910b07207c77f8bfef","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:40:53.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"7a30c37572d0dd2d6d77d175ebccf79cf8177ef1","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:41:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5b4e62a6d4dbf843634914e4ea2c08841da1c0a","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:41:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"416f580161241dc84dabc8d0019b4250f338117f","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:41:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"868691886a995f1680912641777916a614c7e943","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:41:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b5e3cbacb81ab1f8875b237c665fff99ec73bc3","tid":1687313,"uid":68153,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:42:57.000Z","msg":"真係好無說服力<br />\n<br />\n革命始終都係個口號"},{"pid":"c7af40535fde2542cd15ac5014f64cf0a74cee34","tid":1687313,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/revenuetower87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frevenuetower87&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=41a0636a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/revenuetower87</a> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/tax87\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftax87&d=rxvDypeE%2FV4%2FTsysNGkz8PzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=741f4ba5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/tax87</a>"},{"pid":"41fbd2bc7e2cb858c66571fcc8626559570e8701","tid":1687313,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:52:14.000Z","msg":"有次發夢見到有個人好鬼鼠咁用一支好似螺絲批ge野啪一下就爆左行人隧道電梯玻璃 身形都幾大隻<br />\n完事好快咁走左去無跟大隊行無gear<br />\n<br />\n大部分手足會幾個人一組同埋會叫落雨開傘<br />\n上述呢單好有機會係狗做 <br />\n<br />\n如果大家見到有手足/有可疑人士想裝修無障礙設施真係要停一停佢<br />\n啲輪椅人士真係好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a263b951533397a5c31581e5e610ac2781351f1","tid":1687313,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T18:34:09.000Z","msg":"上次影到有便衣警係已清場既地鐵站<br />\n邊個搞事都未知"},{"pid":"5cab4dcd3a936ad125ce5afab392c9c4a5aeb0d3","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c56816c52e3671955b9fdeef95eb216d831435b","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T06:51:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d25dea6f8cbe5e908a59ae4f54b812588675c8c3","tid":1687313,"uid":34978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T06:51:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0dd04577947f9ce2dee5b16e3aa549ef5428cfb2","tid":1687313,"uid":104136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:43:00.000Z","msg":"well said"},{"pid":"5851ea59ee9a5587095fb16f84d07a5e6edb373a","tid":1687313,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:48:55.000Z","msg":"有時未必係巴打做嘅"},{"pid":"1a1cfcb1cb09c08974c8ff1eb52498651d29f0e2","tid":1687313,"uid":118922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:49:59.000Z","msg":"我都明輪椅係幾唔方便，特別係香港啲街又窄、路人又唔太友善、無障礙設施又少"},{"pid":"ecbb534edcb7cbef3379bfb1c8f5a630165dd622","tid":1687313,"uid":105873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T12:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bb6eaf1b39e7182aff57d8d682fdd012e843e3","tid":1687313,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5778bce5bbf7a9a38f465b2f6375e2d0fa49333","tid":1687313,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T06:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5731fb28a267ea147f95f4b7a93efef7c46370","tid":1687313,"uid":169074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}